{
  "stem": "14867.5",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I started to work for a firm.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they liked my legs, so they-- I started to model and become a food-- food model.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they are very, very nice to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Gave me, every week, a raise.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I started with $5.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was-- so the farm was near Princeton, so I used to commute to the city by train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Feliks ?] would take me and pick me up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one day I came.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I found him dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So, as a matter of fact, we were getting ready for a party.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And [INAUDIBLE] lived in the same area.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we tried to become friends with all the artists-- it was artist colony.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And so it was Friday night, and instead of the party, I find him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Heart attack.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so then I-- so going back to my sister.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I came to Canada, I started to-- to again, see if how first I can bring her.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Oh, first, I brought her to Paris.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, also, I was lucky because-- thanks to my brother and his connections from before the war-- through some Jewish guy that he knew, they helped me to-- with an apartment that was impossible to get at that time in Paris, on the suburbs, an apartment, because you couldn't simply get anything.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so he was expecting-- one Jewish guy-- was expecting his family to come, also, survivors to stay in this place that he had for them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he allowed us to stay until they came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had a chance to-- to bring-- that was a good occasion-- to bring my sister and her family, her husband, and the most beautiful child.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then I went-- when I went to Canada, I brought her to Canada.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
